.TH cportage 3 "" "cportage @CP_VERSION@" cportage
.SH "NAME"
cportage \- \fBportage\fR(5)-compatible C library
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.nf
.B #include <cportage.h>
.fi
.SH "MAKE.CONF VARIABLES"
.TP
This section describes cportage-specific make.conf variables.
.TP
\fBCPORTAGE_VARTREE_LAZY\fR = \fI[bool]\fR
If \fItrue\fR (default), CPVartree operates in lazy mode and loads package
metadata on demand.
.SH "ENVIRONMENT OPTIONS"
.TP
\fBCPORTAGE_SHELLCONFIG_DEBUG\fR = \fI[bool]\fR
Enables debug output in shell-like config parser
.TP
\fBCPORTAGE_ATOMPARSER_DEBUG\fR = \fI[bool]\fR
Enables debug output in atom parser
.SH "AUTHORS"
.nf
Marat Radchenko <marat@slonopotamus.org>
.fi
